[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    204[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mProblem:[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;191;97;106m The recipe's prose identifies treatment leakage and event leakage as fundamental modeling concerns. The Event-Leakage paragraph correctly names the 30-60 minute lookahead boundary as essential. The Treatment-Leakage paragraph correctly names the "restrict the model to features available at decision time only" mitigation. This is exactly right.[K
