[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    137[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   3. **The rules_fired list embeds clinical-context details.** When the protocol rule fires "metformin_maintenance_a1c_in_range," the rule_fire embeds the A1c value that supported the decision. When the protocol rule fires "no_dose_change_in_3_months," the rule_fire embeds the dose-change-history. When the rule fires "established_prescriber_authority," the rule_fire embeds the prescriber identity. These are clinical-context elements with their own access-control profile.
