ate_config_assets, tool_call_archive, refill_event_data_archive), subsections to insert, and per-cohort launch-gate metrics. The verdict logic, stage-1/stage-2/stage-3 structure, and recipe-distinct primitives (controlled-substance triple-defense, medication-resolution-against-patient-list safety floor, lab-reconciliation as architectural stage, refill-event-journal as clinical-record class) are all thoroughly addressed."}